'''Weapons Testing Area 34''' was the target zone for a battery of field missile launchers on the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] training [[Planet/Legends|world]] of [[Sirpar/Legends|Sirpar]].

Some time during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]] a band of [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] [[Infiltrators/Legends|infiltrators]] who had stolen a number of crates containing spare parts for [[Starship/Legends|starships]] and an [[Ubrikkian Transports/Legends|Ubrikkian]] [[SuperHaul]] from [[Nonessential Equipment Storage and Disposal Facility 456]] were chased into the testing area by pursuing [[Scout trooper/Legends|scout troopers]] on [[Speeder bike/Legends|speeder bikes]]. The Rebels were able to steer their way through the rain of [[Concussion missile/Legends|concussion missiles]] and made it to the designated pick-up point.

